title: Billy Eichner Proves No One Really Knows Who Chris Pratt Is
text: Billy Eichner Proves No One Really Knows Who Chris Pratt Is Chris Pratt is everywhere these days. But apparently, these New Yorkers would rather meet Josh Duhamel.In the latest ... Comment Posted Oct. 13, 2015 at 11:10 AM Updated at 2:42 PM Posted Oct. 13, 2015 at 11:10 AM Updated at 2:42 PM Â» Social News Chris Pratt is everywhere these days. But apparently, these New Yorkers would rather meet Josh Duhamel. In the latest Billy on the Street clip, Billy Eichner runs around with the Jurassic World star asking strangers: "This is one of the biggest stars in the world right now. Who is it?" "He's from VH1?" one man guesses. "Liam?" another ventures. "F--- if I know," one man admits. Billy Eichner challenged Tina Fey to name 20 Latinos on Billy on the Street But the best part of the video is when Eichner tells a woman in a raincoat that Pratt is Las Vegas star Josh Duhamel, prompting the woman to jump up and down, shouting, "Awesome!" We have no idea how Pratt's ego is handling all of this, but we bet Josh Duhamel is having his best day in years.
